name: He Is Not Ready
Lore: '''All his live has he looked away. To the future, to the horizon. Never his mind on where he was! Hmm? What he was doing! Hm.''',
Text: 'Deploy on any character. Subtracts 2 from that character''s training destiny draws. OR Deploy on an opponent''s pilot at a site. During each of opponent''s move phases, opponent must choose to move that character, lose that character or lose 1 Force.',
